---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | ToolPolaris"
  description="ToolPolaris privacy policy — what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights."
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-sub">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-page">

      <p class="lead">ToolPolaris takes your privacy seriously. This policy explains what data we collect, why we collect it, and how you can control it.</p>

      <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Analytics data.</strong> We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how visitors use the site. This includes pages visited, time on site, device type, and approximate location (country/city level). This data is aggregated and does not personally identify you.</p>
      <p><strong>Newsletter subscriptions.</strong> If you subscribe to the Polaris Pro newsletter, we collect your email address. We use this solely to send you the newsletter and related communications you requested.</p>
      <p><strong>Contact form submissions.</strong> If you contact us via the contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message content to respond to your enquiry.</p>
      <p><strong>Cookies.</strong> We use cookies for analytics (Google Analytics) and to remember your preferences. You can decline non-essential cookies via the cookie notice on your first visit.</p>

      <h2>2. How we use your information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To understand site usage and improve content</li>
        <li>To send the newsletter you subscribed to</li>
        <li>To respond to contact form submissions</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your personal data. We do not use your data for advertising targeting.</p>

      <h2>3. Third-party services</h2>
      <p>ToolPolaris uses the following third-party services that may process your data according to their own privacy policies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> &mdash; website analytics</li>
        <li><strong>Beehiiv</strong> &mdash; newsletter delivery</li>
        <li><strong>Netlify</strong> &mdash; website hosting</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Affiliate links on this site direct you to third-party websites with their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for their data practices.</p>

      <h2>4. Data retention</h2>
      <p>Analytics data is retained for 14 months as per Google Analytics defaults. Email addresses are retained until you unsubscribe. Contact form data is retained for 12 months.</p>

      <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or export your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact us at the address below.</p>

      <h2>6. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related enquiries: <a href="/contact/">use our contact form</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: var(--brand-dark); padding: 64px 0 52px; }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin: 10px 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
  .page-sub { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

  .prose-page { max-width: 740px; }
  .lead { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 2em; font-weight: 500; }
  .prose-page h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--brand-dark); margin: 2em 0 0.6em; }
  .prose-page p  { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 1em; }
  .prose-page ul { margin: 0.6em 0 1em 1.4em; }
  .prose-page li { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.3em; }
  .prose-page strong { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 700; }
  .prose-page a { color: var(--brand-accent); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  .prose-page a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
